[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0875","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0875.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1023","title":"Sun Solaris useradd 账户过期日期绕过漏洞","description":"Solaris 7.0 系统中的 useradd 命令在解析 \"-e\"（账户过期日期）参数时，未能正确处理特定日期格式，当系统管理员或具有相应权限的用户使用某些非常规日期格式设置账户过期时间时，useradd 会错误地忽略或误解该设置，导致账户在过期后仍可正常登录系统。该漏洞影响 Solaris 7.0 版本，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。攻击者需拥有本地账户并利用特定的日期格式参数即可绕过账户过期限制，获取非授权系统访问权限。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1023"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-06-10T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:32.613","remediation":"建议升级到 Solaris 8 或更高版本以彻底修复该问题。如无法升级，按 Sun 官方提供的解决方案替换 /etc/datemsk 配置文件，增加 %m/%d/%Y 等四位数年份格式（大写 %Y）使 useradd -e 能正确解析\"2000\"等四位年份，避免将 6/30/2000 误判为 2020 年。另外在创建账户后手动用 `logins -x` 验证到期日期是否正确，作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92904175406756&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/426","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2765cfa5d0fc39151c354509f5ba2b7abfdb61de/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1023.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1023","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1023.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1023.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1023.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/solaris7_110869.nasl","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-mc67-m38f-vc3q/GHSA-mc67-m38f-vc3q.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/jdkoftinoff/mb-linux-msli/blob/8adb103e34af9ff1d8d122e9ee2a1808836f0a14/uClinux-dist/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/solaris7_x86_110870.nasl","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/426/info.html"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0875.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0706","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0706.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0775","title":"思科 IOS 千兆交换机路由器访问控制绕过漏洞","description":"运行 Cisco IOS 的思科千兆交换机路由器存在访问控制缺陷，远程攻击者可通过向目标设备发送特制数据包绕过 ACL 规则，实现未经授权的数据包转发。该漏洞影响运行 IOS 的思科千兆交换机路由器系列产品，攻击者无需身份认证即可利用，可能导致敏感信息泄露或网络流量被劫持。建议用户及时升级 IOS 版本或配置严格的访问控制列表以缓解风险。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0775"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-06-10","updated":"1999-06-10","remediation":"升级 Cisco IOS 至修复该漏洞的版本（如 12.0(5)XK 及以上），或在 ACL 中避免单独依赖 established 关键字，改用具体端口和协议的显式 permit/deny 规则组合实现访问控制。如无法升级，可在边界路由器上启用基于上下文的访问控制（CBAC）作为替代方案。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/58a0ea900decdd7e971b95fcaa99234de5a5df5e/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0775.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0775","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0775.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/dabf5b9888e8885cf125c5729901a7ad84d00092/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0775.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/18de81c56daca1c9e33223f0b95bdb8312a1ca75/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-vjxr-fvc6-86qw/GHSA-vjxr-fvc6-86qw.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0775.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000670.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87022/info.html"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0706.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1015","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1015.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1231","title":"SSH ssh 用户名枚举漏洞","description":"SSH 2.0.12 及部分其他版本在用户认证过程中存在用户名枚举漏洞。当客户端提供有效用户名时，服务器会提示输入密码并允许多次尝试；而输入无效用户名时仅提示一次即拒绝连接。远程攻击者可利用这一行为差异，通过遍历用户名并观察服务器响应，枚举目标系统上的有效用户账号，为后续暴力破解或针对性攻击提供信息支撑。该漏洞影响 SSH 2.0.12 及相关版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1231"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-06-09T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:59.880","remediation":"升级至 OpenSSH 3.0 及以上版本，该问题已在后续协议实现中得到修复。如无法升级，在 sshd_config 中设置 `MaxAuthTries 1` 限制单连接认证尝试次数，并启用 `LogLevel VERBOSE` 记录认证失败信息辅助审计。建议关闭密码认证 (`PasswordAuthentication no`)，改用公钥认证方式彻底阻断用户名枚举。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/14758","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2276","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ead50dc12e50bdd7f50b53d9d01c9f9946862c44/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1231.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1231","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1231.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1231.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-7g97-5hq7-x7mm/GHSA-7g97-5hq7-x7mm.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87557/info.html","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Exploit-List-Ja/blob/979579ffd61606c64cf772a1e865f5126788e4ec/1999.tsv","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--0457d271-b4c6-4bb2-813d-1cf71d06fee5.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000668.txt","https://github.com/opencve/opencve-kb/blob/80b48aaf24cf1857bcadf6b9d454e9c0f7a850a5/1999/CVE-1999-1231.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1015.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1134","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1134.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1496","title":"Debian Linux 及 Red Hat Sudo 1.5 文件存在性信息泄露漏洞","description":"Sudo 1.5 版本存在本地信息泄露漏洞。本地攻击者可通过尝试将目标文件名作为程序执行来探测任意文件是否存在，当文件不存在时系统会返回不同的错误提示信息，从而泄露文件存在性信息。该漏洞影响 Debian Linux 2.1 和 Red Hat 6.0 等系统，CVSS 评分 2.1，危害等级低。攻击者需拥有本地访问权限，利用条件较为有限。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1496"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-06-08T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:33.947","remediation":"升级 Sudo 至 1.6 及以上版本，该漏洞在 Sudo 1.6 中已修复。对于 Debian 系统，升级至 Debian 3.0 及以上版本；对于 Red Hat 系统，升级至 Red Hat 7.0 及以上版本。如无法升级，可限制本地用户对 sudo 的访问权限，仅允许受信任用户使用 sudo 命令。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/14665","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/321","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2277"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1134.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1134.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0171","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0171.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0493","title":"Sun Solaris rpc.statd RPC调用转发漏洞","description":"Sun Solaris 2.5.1 的 rpc.statd 服务存在 RPC 调用转发漏洞，远程攻击者可通过 SM_MON 和 SM_NOTIFY 命令将伪造的 RPC 调用转发至本地操作系统，进而利用该机制触发 automountd 等其他组件的远程代码执行。该漏洞影响 Sun Solaris 2.5.1 版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高，无需身份认证即可远程利用。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0493"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-06-07T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:30.887","remediation":"升级 Solaris 至 2.6 及以上版本，该漏洞已在后续版本修复。如无法升级，可禁用 rpc.statd 服务（`/etc/init.d/rpc stop; rm /etc/rc3.d/S73nfs.client`），或在防火墙层面阻止外部对 RPC 端口 111/TCP、111/UDP 及 rpc.statd 动态端口的访问。同时建议限制 NFS 仅在内网可信网络使用。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=91547759121289&w=2","http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/186&type=0&nav=sec.sba","http://www.cert.org/advisories/CA-99-05-statd-automountd.html","http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/j-045.shtml","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/450","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19327"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0171.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1806","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1806.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1237","title":"Apache smbval SMB认证库 缓冲区溢出远程代码执行漏洞","description":"smbvalid/smbval SMB 认证库存在多处缓冲区溢出漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向使用该库的模块（如 Apache::AuthenSmb）发送特制的超长用户名或密码，触发缓冲区溢出，进而执行任意命令。CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。受影响的系统包括所有使用了受影响版本 smbvalid/smbval 库的 Web 服务器及应用，攻击者无需身份认证即可远程利用。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1237"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-06-06T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:00.657","remediation":"立即停止使用已停止维护的 smbvalid/smbval SMB 认证库及 Apache::AuthenSmb 模块，迁移至 Apache 官方支持的 mod_authnz_ldap 模块通过 LDAP/LDAPS 协议对接 Active Directory 或 Samba DC 完成认证；如仍需 SMB 认证，可改用 Samba Winbind 结合 mod_authnz_ldap 实现，所有输入参数必须经过严格的长度校验与转义处理。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/14384","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2272","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ead50dc12e50bdd7f50b53d9d01c9f9946862c44/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1237.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1237","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1237.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1237.json","https://github.com/openembedded/meta-openembedded/blob/e93799db0e7c7b23da8a00891403425ae7e87d7b/meta-webserver/recipes-httpd/apache2/apache2_2.4.68.bb","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-65fj-56w9-gr9r/GHSA-65fj-56w9-gr9r.json","https://github.com/apache/calcite-avatica/blob/b8bc167268d0900087a24eecd150e8911a6225c0/src/main/config/dependency-check/suppressions.xml","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87828/info.html","https://github.com/anchore/cve-data-enrichment/blob/61a6f60f73f6727dfcef688b4834f32c678de1b5/data/anchore/1999/CVE-1999-1237.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153500_153600.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1806.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0757","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0757.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0970","title":"Omnicron OmniHTTPD visadmin.exe 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Omnicron OmniHTTPD 1.1 及 2.0 版本中的 visadmin.exe 管理程序存在拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证，仅通过向目标服务器发送精心构造的恶意 URL 请求，即可触发该程序在服务器上大量生成临时文件，迅速耗尽磁盘空间或系统资源，最终导致 Web 服务崩溃或无法响应正常请求。该漏洞影响运行 OmniHTTPD 1.1 与 2.0 Alpha 1 版本的 Windows 系统，CVSS 评分为 5.0，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0970"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-06-05T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:25.977","remediation":"OmniHTTPD 产品已停止维护，官方未发布补丁。建议立即停用 OmniHTTPD 并迁移至活跃维护的 Web 服务器（如 Apache httpd、Nginx）。临时缓解措施：在 Web 服务器或防火墙层面阻止对 /visadmin.exe 的外部访问请求，限制 Web 服务运行账户对临时文件目录的写入权限，降低被利用风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/14311","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1808","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2271","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20304"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0757.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0757.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0757.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1098","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1098.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1400","title":"经济学人 1999 屏幕保护程序 安全绕过漏洞","description":"The Economist 1999 屏幕保护程序在启用\"密码保护\"选项后存在安全绕过漏洞。具有物理访问权限的攻击者可在屏幕锁定状态下通过运行 Internet Explorer 绕过屏保密码保护，从而读取受保护的文件。该漏洞影响 The Economist 1999 屏幕保护程序版本，攻击者需具备本地物理访问条件，CVSS 评分 2.1，危害等级低。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1400"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-06-03T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:21.577","remediation":"该屏幕保护程序已停止维护，建议立即卸载 The Economist 1999 Screen Saver，改用操作系统自带的屏幕锁定功能（Windows 按 Win+L 锁定）。如必须使用，可在组策略中禁用 Internet Explorer 在锁屏状态下的运行权限作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://archives.indenial.com/hypermail/ntbugtraq/1999/June1999/0007.html","http://archives.indenial.com/hypermail/ntbugtraq/1999/June1999/00