中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1412"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-06-03T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:23.160","remediation":"升级 Apache HTTP Server 至 1.3.14 及以上版本，或升级 Mac OS X 至 10.1 及以上版本以修复该拒绝服务漏洞。如无法升级，可在 Apache 配置中启用 mod_limitipconn 模块限制单 IP 并发连接数，或在防火墙层面限制 CGI 路径的请求速率作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/14215","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/306","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19244","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/6e5939e8074723d33adaf5b2f8b0352edab9ba8d/1999/CVE-1999-1412.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ad01ef67b360e9139b8072c8e614b7c7c1f658d2/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1412.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1412","https://github.com/Indie365/cbl-mariner/blob/80d864c0a617439675510c037c8a4589aa596fbb/SPECS/httpd/CVE-1999-1412.nopatch","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/1d279cde1e5f7d9e150ca373126c9b35476ad3f5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1412.json","https://github.com/openbmc/openbmc/blob/dfcbe94d5079fa41425f282cc25e5f96c2e1f39b/upstream-layers/meta-openembedded/meta-webserver/recipes-httpd/apache2/apache2_2.4.68.bb","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1412.md","https://github.com/ericpattison/Mariner/blob/6b6b870716931ff24c71b575ecd690aa7979fdd6/CBL-Mariner/SPECS/httpd/CVE-1999-1412.nopatch","https://github.com/anchore/nvd-data-overrides/blob/591cd0ec0d112aca806ccf6026dc26bcd4943be7/data/1999/CVE-1999-1412.json","https://github.com/openembedded/meta-openembedded/blob/e93799db0e7c7b23da8a00891403425ae7e87d7b/meta-webserver/recipes-httpd/apache2/apache2_2.4.68.bb"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1101.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-1101.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1101.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0499","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0499.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0772","title":"Compaq Insight Management Agent 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Compaq Insight Management Agent 服务存在拒绝服务漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标系统的 2301 端口发送超长字符串，触发服务组件缓冲区溢出，导致 Compaq Management Agents 及 Survey Utility 服务崩溃或无法响应。该漏洞影响 Compaq 系列服务器管理软件，攻击者无需身份认证即可利用，CVSS 评分 6.4，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.4,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0772"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-06-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:01.590","remediation":"立即升级 Compaq Insight Management Agent 至厂商修复版本（1999 年已发布补丁），或卸载 Compaq Survey Utility。如无法升级，在防火墙上封禁 TCP 端口 2301 的入站访问，仅允许受信任管理站点的 IP 地址连接该端口。若业务不再需要该管理服务，建议直接禁用或卸载 Compaq Management Agents 服务以彻底消除风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0772","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/58a0ea900decdd7e971b95fcaa99234de5a5df5e/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0772.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0772","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0772.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/dabf5b9888e8885cf125c5729901a7ad84d00092/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0772.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/18de81c56daca1c9e33223f0b95bdb8312a1ca75/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-545v-66g8-w7vj/GHSA-545v-66g8-w7vj.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0772.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000656.txt","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_dos.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0499.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0546","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0546.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0804","title":"Linux Linux内核 ICMP报文 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Linux Kernel 2.2.x 内核的 ICMP 协议处理逻辑存在缺陷，远程攻击者可向目标系统发送包含异常类型、代码及畸变 IP 头长度的特制 ICMP 数据包，触发内核处理异常而导致拒绝服务。该漏洞无需认证即可远程触发，影响 Debian Linux 2.1、RedHat Linux 6.0、SuSE Linux 6.1 等发行版，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0804"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-06-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:05.527","remediation":"升级 Linux 内核至 2.4.0 或更高版本（该漏洞在 2.3.x 开发系列中已修复，2.4.0 正式版已彻底解决畸形 ICMP 包处理问题）。临时缓解措施：在网络边界防火墙配置规则，丢弃异常的 ICMP 类型和代码的报文，如禁止 ICMP 类型 13/14/17/18 等罕见类型的入站流量。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/302","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19241"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0546.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1688","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1688.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1063","title":"CdomainFree whois_raw.cgi 远程命令执行漏洞","description":"tags.<value>CdomainFree 2.4 的 whois_raw.cgi CGI 脚本中存在命令注入漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向 fqdn 参数提交包含 shell 元字符的特制请求，在目标服务器上以 Web 服务器权限执行任意命令。该漏洞 CVSS 评分为 10.0，危害等级严重，攻击无需身份认证，可导致服务器完全受控。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1063"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-06-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:37.747","remediation":"由于 CdomainFree 2.4 已停止维护，建议立即删除或禁用 whois_raw.cgi 脚本，或在 Web 服务器（Apache/Nginx）层面限制该脚本仅允许可信 IP 访问。同时在 CGI 参数处理中严格过滤 shell 元字符（; | & ` $ ( ) { } < >），并对 fqdn 参数实施白名单验证（仅允许域名合法字符），从根本上防止命令注入。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/14019","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/304","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2251","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19242","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/297eb115816d3735806f02ee33bb4d2d53ecd5c6/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1063.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1063","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1063.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1063.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1063.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/whois_raw.nasl","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/304/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153500_153600.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1063.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_3.list.dict"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1688.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-1688.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1688.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1130","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1130.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1485","title":"SGI IRIX nsd 信息泄露漏洞","description":"SGI IRIX 6.5 至 6.5.2 版本中的 nsd（名称服务守护进程）存在信息泄露漏洞。该服务在 UDP 端口上导出一个虚拟文件系统，远程攻击者无需认证即可通过网络挂载该虚拟文件系统，从而读取目标系统上的任意文件，并可能造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 SGI IRIX 6.5、6.5.1 及 6.5.2 版本，CVSS v2 评分 6.4，危害等级中危。攻击者只需向目标 UDP 端口发送特制请求即可利用，无需任何身份认证。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1485"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-05-31","updated":"1999-05-31","remediation":"升级 SGI IRIX 至 6.5.3 或更高版本，该版本已修复 nsd 信息泄露漏洞。如无法升级，可在 /etc/inetd.conf 中注释掉 nsd 服务行并重启 inetd 以禁用该服务，或通过防火墙限制对 nsd 端口（默认 80/443）的访问。作为临时缓解措施，可移除 nsd 的 world-readable 权限：chmod 750 /usr/ns-home/nsd。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19316"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1130.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0883","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0883.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1028","title":"Symantec pcAnywhere 8.0 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Symantec pcAnywhere 8.0 存在拒绝服务漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向 5631 端口发送大量数据，导致目标系统 CPU 利用率急剧飙升，造成服务不可用。该漏洞影响 Symantec pcAnywhere 8.0 版本，攻击者无需认证即可远程发起攻击，对业务连续性造成严重影响。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1028"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-05-28","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级至 Symantec pcAnywhere 9.0 或更高版本。如无法升级，在网络边界防火墙和主机防火墙中限制 TCP 5631 端口的入站访问，仅允许受信任 IP 地址连接。对内部网络中的 pcAnywhere 服务实施访问控制列表（ACL），并禁用不必要的远程控制功能。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=92807524225090&w=2","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/2256.php","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/288"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0883.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0467","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0467.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0755","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 RRAS 和 RAS 拨号网络密码缓存漏洞","description":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 的 RAS（远程访问服务）拨号网络功能存在凭据管理漏洞，即使用户未勾选\"保存密码\"选项，系统仍会将用户密码明文缓存在本地注册表或配置文件中。本地已登录攻击者可通过读取系统缓存获取其他用户的登录凭据，进而实现权限提升或横向移动。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 全系列版本（SP0 至 SP5），CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0755"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-05-27T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:59.367","remediation":"升级到 Windows 2000 或更高版本操作系统，Windows NT 4.0 已停止支持且不再发布安全更新。如无法升级，通过注册表设置 HKLM\\SYSTEM\\CurrentControlSet\\Services\\RasMan\\Parameters\\DisableSavePassword 为 1 以禁用 RAS 密码缓存功能。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ230681","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-017","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19196","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/6e5939e8074723d33adaf5b2f8b0352edab9ba8d/1999/CVE-1999-0755.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ad01ef67b360e9139b8072c8e614b7c7c1f658d2/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0755.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0755","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/1d279cde1e5f7d9e150ca373126c9b35476ad3f5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0755.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0755.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/18de81c56daca1c9e33223f0b95bdb8312a1ca75/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-g6q4-7rrm-ppv6/GHSA-g6q4-7rrm-ppv6.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef